1. *Važan* je da budemo srećni. (It is important to be happy.)
2. On je *važan* član porodice. (He is an important member of the family.)
3. Ona je *važna* osoba u našem životu. (She is an important person in our life.)
4. *Važni* su nam prijatelji. (Our friends are important to us.)
5. Porodica je *važna* za našu budućnost. (Family is important for our future.)